[I] A modified version of dhcpcd to use scripts

[T] dhcpcd-scriptconfig is a modified version of dhcpcd designed to do all
[T] configuration with scripts. The goals are to make a fully extensible
[T] DHCP client, to simplify the code inside of the DHCP client itself,
[T] and to improve platform independence
[T]
